This is a sample guideline on how NOFL should be built.

There are many main products that can be built out of NOFL:

   1) Management tools (nofl-manager)
   2) Management Library (libnoflmanager)
   3) Certificate Validation Library (linoflvalidation)
   4) Python Certificatie Validation module (noflvalidationmodule.so)
   5) PHP Certificatie Validation module (noflvalidationmodule.c)
   

